  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK976">
<l>ciṟiyā ruṇarcciyu ḷillai periyāraip</l>
<l>pēṇikkoḷ vēmeṉṉu nōkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is never in the nature of the base to seek the society of the great and partake of their nature.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
